Project #:  27 





 











UCI Marketplace 



Project #:  27 




Members:Varun Shenoy, Persis Shah, Aneesh Rajan Thakur, Venkata Sai Abhishek Kandikattu






Description:A secure, clean, multi-functional, web application that allows only authenticated UCI students to buy or sell products in an online marketplace, search for products, get in touch with the seller, and pay to buy whatever they like. Students can buy in-app, through the seller, or use the AI Driven Chatbot to navigate through the app.





